 .
 This package is part of KDE, and a component of the KDE libraries module.
 See the 'kde' and 'kdelibs' packages for more information.

Package: kdelibs-bin
Architecture: any
Depends: ${shlibs:Depends}
Conflicts: kjscmd
Description: executables for all KDE 4 core applications
 This package contains common executables used by all KDE 4 applications.
 .
 This package is part of KDE, and a component of the KDE libraries module.
 See the 'kde' and 'kdelibs' packages for more information.

Package: kdelibs-dbg
Section: libdevel
Architecture: any
Priority: extra
Depends: kdelibs5 (= ${binary:Version}), libqt4-debug, libc6-dbg [amd64]
Description: debugging symbols for kdelibs
 This package contains the debugging symbols associated with kdelibs.
 They will automatically be used by gdb for debugging kdelibs-related
 issues.

Package: libphonon-dev
Section: libdevel
Architecture: any
Depends: libphonon4 (= ${binary:Version})
Replaces: kdelibs5-dev (<< 4:3.98.0~svn755919-1)
Description: cross-platform multimedia framework (development)
 Phonon is a cross-platform multimedia framework that enables the use of audio
 and video content in Qt and KDE 4 applications.
 .
 This package contains development files necessary to build applications that
 use Phonon.

Package: libphonon4
Section: libs
Architecture: any
Depends: ${shlibs:Depends}, ${misc:Depends}
Replaces: kdelibs5 (<< 4:3.98.0~svn755919-1)
Description: cross-platform multimedia framework
 Phonon is a cross-platform multimedia framework that enables the use of audio
 and video content in Qt and KDE 4 applications.
 .
 This package contains the files necessary to run applications that use Phonon.
